{
  "message": "fix(io): remove trailing comma from single-element shape tuple formatting\n\nFix format string for shape tuples to output \"(N)\" instead of \"(N,)\"\nwhen serializing single-element shapes, matching NumPy's npy format\nspecification for header metadata.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
